[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/ogust"]
[Student "S"]
{Having opened 2\D, you reply to partner's Ogust 2NT bid with 3NT, showing a \D suit headed by A K Q. Partner passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
